                        <interp inst="t18731215-76-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18731215-76-punishment-17" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18731215-76-punishment-17" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18731215-76-punishment-17" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-76-18731215 t18731215-76-punishment-17"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment. There was another indictment against the prisoner</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
